  <section>
    <h2>⏱️ Telemetry</h2>
    <pre>| Wave | Tasks | Duration | Verify | Retries | Tokens | Cost |
|------|-------|----------|--------|---------|--------|------|
| 1 | 1 | 1.5s | 250ms | 1 | 100 | 0.50 |
| 2 | 1 | 500ms | — | 0 | 25 | — |
